1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,980
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 3 =

20
00:01:33,020 --> 00:01:39,820
= Yan Mansion =

21
00:01:40,860 --> 00:01:42,860
The test of the Ministry of Rites
will be held next month.

22
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:46,620
=Yan Shu, courtesy name Tongshu =
The reorganization of the national history

23
00:01:47,020 --> 00:01:48,220
has just started yet.

24
00:01:49,380 --> 00:01:52,900
If I leave, I don’t think I can manage it.

25
00:01:55,100 --> 00:01:56,340
I let the prime minister down.

26
00:01:59,140 --> 00:02:00,300
Once I leave the capital,

27
00:02:00,940 --> 00:02:01,900
I’ll give the two antique ink sticks

28
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:03,980
to him as an apology.

29
00:02:05,580 --> 00:02:07,820
Then where are we going now?

30
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:11,260
I don’t know.

31
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:12,540
Let’s wait for the Emperor’s decree.

32
00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:15,340
Will it be the wild land?

33
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:18,540
The decree hasn’t arrived yet,

34
00:02:18,660 --> 00:02:20,460
how can you know we are leaving?

35
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:24,380
I’ve been studying the philosophy of metaphysics,

36
00:02:24,540 --> 00:02:25,660
and I’ve learnt a lot.

37
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:28,860
I’ve divined yesterday

38
00:02:30,220 --> 00:02:33,140
and found we’ll have to leave the capital today.

39
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:34,940
Sir,

40
00:02:35,340 --> 00:02:36,860
can you divine where we will go?

41
00:02:40,620 --> 00:02:41,660
I didn’t learn enough

42
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:44,100
to predict everything.

43
00:02:48,820 --> 00:02:49,900
I’ll have a walk outside.

44
00:02:51,900 --> 00:02:53,220
I’ll get you an umbrella.

45
00:02:55,180 --> 00:02:55,940
No need.

46
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:03,140
Sir.

47
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:05,660
= Zhao Zhen =
Are you going to teach me poetry on winter sweet?

48
00:03:06,580 --> 00:03:08,540
Good poems are gifts from the God.

49
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:11,780
Today I’m not going to talk about poems with you.

50
00:03:12,140 --> 00:03:13,340
We’ll just wander in the snow,

51
00:03:14,260 --> 00:03:15,580
pick some flowers

52
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:17,300
and collect a jar of the snow on flowers.

53
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:19,460
Ask the kitchen to make some tea with the snow,

54
00:03:20,060 --> 00:03:22,500
and some cookies with winter sweet as stuffing

55
00:03:22,980 --> 00:03:24,580
winter sweet cookies

56
00:03:28,020 --> 00:03:33,380
♪ A sallow passes by my window ♪

57
00:03:34,660 --> 00:03:39,820
♪ Red petals falls in the pavilion ♪

58
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:47,380
♪ Coldness covers me beside the handrail ♪

59
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:53,140
♪ Green curtain is revealed by the winds ♪

60
00:03:55,260 --> 00:04:00,060
♪ Several raindrops drip on the lotus leaves ♪

61
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:03,580
♪ Everyone’s gone after sobering up ♪

62
00:04:07,180 --> 00:04:11,900
♪ Only the loneliness fills the air ♪

63
00:04:24,260 --> 00:04:25,140
The Empress Dowager said

64
00:04:26,060 --> 00:04:27,700
“I’ve read your letter.

65
00:04:28,180 --> 00:04:29,820
I now declare to have Yan Shu

66
00:04:29,820 --> 00:04:31,300
accompanying me to the Yuqing Taoist Temple.”

67
00:04:38,980 --> 00:04:40,500
Yes, Your Majesty.

68
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:52,020
= Yuqing Taoist Temple =

69
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:07,540
My lord, I’ve received the oral message

70
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:08,500
and bring it to you without delay.

71
00:05:09,860 --> 00:05:10,540
Idiot!

72
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:12,420
Why does it take you so long?

73
00:05:17,260 --> 00:05:18,460
What are they arguing about?

74
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:21,940
= Ren Shouzhong, courtesy name Jichen =

75
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:29,740
= April 1027 A.D.
Deputy Executive, Yan Shu’s Report =

76
00:05:32,700 --> 00:05:33,580
Your Majesty,

77
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:36,300
Yan Shu came here after being summoned.

78
00:05:36,740 --> 00:05:38,700
He punished the attendant with the court board

79
00:05:38,980 --> 00:05:41,260
for sending him the board too late.

80
00:05:42,540 --> 00:05:43,460
The attendant fell

81
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:45,420
and broke his front teeth.

82
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:50,380
Yan Shu punished the attendant outside the hall?

83
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:54,060
Yan Shu

84
00:05:55,580 --> 00:05:57,100
is indeed a talent

85
00:05:57,100 --> 00:05:58,620
late Emperor selected for His Majesty.

86
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:06,620
What a man.

87
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:12,540
Summoned by the Majesty,

88
00:06:12,860 --> 00:06:15,140
Yan Shu asked someone to fetch his board,
and he was late.

89
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:17,140
He let the Majesty wait for a subordinate.

90
00:06:17,260 --> 00:06:18,300
That is disrespect.

91
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:21,300
He was furious and hurt his attendant carelessly.

92
00:06:21,540 --> 00:06:22,580
That is not his intention.

93
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:24,940
= Wang Zeng, courtesy name Xiaoxian=
Admonition and salary deduction are enough.

94
00:06:25,060 --> 00:06:27,140
He does not deserve to be evicted.

95
00:06:30,460 --> 00:06:31,980
Yan Shu is the prime minister,

96
00:06:32,540 --> 00:06:33,580
leading all the vassals.

97
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:35,780
Yet his fury disgraced his manner.

98
00:06:36,060 --> 00:06:38,340
So he should be punished strictly to warn others.

99
00:06:38,900 --> 00:06:41,260
How can we just treat him with salary deduction?

100
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:44,580
Please punish him
according to the law to show justice.

101
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:48,500
Please punish him
according to the law to show justice.

102
00:06:53,340 --> 00:06:54,220
I’m still young.

103
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:56,060
This is about a major official at the court.

104
00:06:56,860 --> 00:06:58,140
I would like to give this decision to my mother.

105
00:07:00,540 --> 00:07:02,100
Managing the country is like balancing
a pair of scales.

106
00:07:03,300 --> 00:07:05,420
Balance it with justice,

107
00:07:06,580 --> 00:07:07,980
otherwise it will tilt.

108
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:11,100
Instability tops the list of threats to a country.

109
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:12,900
Therefore,

110
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:15,340
I have to make a choice

111
00:07:15,660 --> 00:07:16,940
to ensure the balance.

112
00:07:17,900 --> 00:07:19,820
The prime minister is loyal and righteous.

113
00:07:20,540 --> 00:07:21,780
He’s able and talented.

114
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:24,860
He became famous when he was young,

115
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:27,380
which breeds his arrogance.

116
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:30,300
= Xia Song, courtesy name Ziqiao =
He despises mediocre people,

117
00:07:30,540 --> 00:07:31,700
and treats people too harshly.

118
00:07:32,780 --> 00:07:34,100
This severe punishment

119
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,700
is not just to warn all the vassals,

120
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:41,180
but also to remove his arrogance.

121
00:07:42,340 --> 00:07:43,740
Yan Shu lost his manners,

122
00:07:44,380 --> 00:07:46,300
disqualifying him as a lead of all the vassals.

123
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:52,260
Demote him as the vice Chief Executive
of Privy Council, the Vice Minister of Justice.

124
00:07:52,660 --> 00:07:54,100
Send him to Nanjing.

125
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:56,820
Governor of Huai’an

126
00:07:57,060 --> 00:07:59,940
and the consultant of the cabinet and ministry
of supervision, Zhang Qi

127
00:08:00,420 --> 00:08:02,100
is honest and prudent.

128
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:03,460
He made great contributions to the country.

129
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:05,700
Promote him as the Chief Executive
of Privy Council.

130
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:10,660
What do you think, Your Majesty?

131
00:08:13,780 --> 00:08:16,140
That is the proper treatment.

132
00:08:17,060 --> 00:08:18,620
Civil Servant Examination
of the Ministry of Rites is coming.

133
00:08:19,460 --> 00:08:20,740
Yan Shu will leave the capital,

134
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,420
Wang Zeng is old.

135
00:08:22,940 --> 00:08:26,380
I’d like to bother Lv Yijian to help this time.

136
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:56,180
= House of Yan =

137
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:04,060
Sir, you are in a good mood.

138
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:11,940
Your Majesty has come to the study

139
00:09:12,980 --> 00:09:14,220
yet I didn’t notice.

140
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:15,580
I didn’t manage the house strictly.

141
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:17,700
Please punish me.

142
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:19,220
What punishment can I give you now?

143
00:09:19,780 --> 00:09:21,860
You’ve been evicted to Nanjing,

144
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:22,860
should I demote you down another level

145
00:09:23,060 --> 00:09:24,260
before you leave?

146
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:26,180
Alright, no need to be polite to me.

147
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:28,740
I told them not to tell.

148
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:31,260
Otherwise I’ll punish them.

149
00:09:33,820 --> 00:09:34,820
Don’t be nervous, sir.

150
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:37,580
I just have one thing unclear

151
00:09:37,740 --> 00:09:38,660
and would like to ask for your opinion.

152
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:40,980
Please tell, Your Majesty.

153
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:47,140
The Analects of Confucius says

154
00:09:47,740 --> 00:09:50,060
one day, Zilu is staying in Rock Gate.

155
00:09:50,780 --> 00:09:51,860
The second morning,

156
00:09:52,340 --> 00:09:53,580
The doorkeeper asks who he is.

157
00:09:54,380 --> 00:09:55,300
He replies

158
00:09:55,660 --> 00:09:57,420
he’s disciple of Confucius.

159
00:09:57,980 --> 00:09:59,660
The doorkeeper nods his head and says

160
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:01,460
you are

161
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:03,460
the disciple of Confucius

162
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:04,460
who attempts the impossible.

163
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:06,780
People always call

164
00:10:06,780 --> 00:10:08,700
the disciples of Confucius

165
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:10,180
as those who attempt the impossible.

166
00:10:11,060 --> 00:10:12,460
You are also a disciple of Confucius,

167
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:15,860
but you argued with
Empress Dowager about Zhang Qi.

168
00:10:16,620 --> 00:10:18,340
You knew she wouldn’t allow it,

169
00:10:18,940 --> 00:10:20,460
so you packed your luggage

170
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:23,340
prepared yourself for leaving the capital.

171
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:25,460
But you refuse to obey against your will.

172
00:10:26,060 --> 00:10:27,780
That is to attempt the impossible,

173
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:28,980
right?

174
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:33,340
Then I have a question.

175
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:35,700
What is the impossible?

176
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:37,820
If they are the bad things,

177
00:10:38,220 --> 00:10:39,340
then we shouldn’t do it.

178
00:10:39,660 --> 00:10:41,140
If they are the good things,

179
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:43,820
but the Emperor made them

180
00:10:43,820 --> 00:10:45,180
the impossible,

181
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:47,860
then the Emperor is fatuous,

182
00:10:48,780 --> 00:10:49,660
isn’t he?

183
00:10:53,780 --> 00:10:55,100
I lost my manner again,

184
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,420
I’m so sorry.

185
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:57,860
This time, I can make the decision

186
00:10:58,260 --> 00:10:59,300
to pardon you.

187
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:03,340
The world is big enough to contain everything.

188
00:11:03,500 --> 00:11:06,340
The evil accompanies the good,
Yin accompanies Yang.

189
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:09,100
You are the master of the world,

190
00:11:09,260 --> 00:11:11,940
not the swordsman or the judge who

191
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:12,900
upholds the good and punishes the evil.

192
00:11:13,940 --> 00:11:15,260
What should a wise emperor do?

193
00:11:17,940 --> 00:11:19,620
Managing the country is like balancing a pair of scales.

194
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:21,140
If you want to keep the balance,

195
00:11:21,260 --> 00:11:22,740
you should keep your heart clear as a mirror,

196
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,540
able to tell right from wrong.

197
00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:27,420
You must have strong arms

198
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:29,020
to hold the scale

199
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:31,180
to balance all the powers within the country.

200
00:11:31,580 --> 00:11:32,420
Now I

201
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:34,500
can’t be your arm anymore

202
00:11:34,660 --> 00:11:36,380
to undertake Empress Dowager’s strength.

203
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:38,740
But I’ll still contribute whatever I have left

204
00:11:39,060 --> 00:11:40,580
to clear your mind,

205
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:43,860
to tell all the vassals what is right and wrong.

206
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:47,060
I was evicted this time

207
00:11:47,060 --> 00:11:48,180
for disgracing myself,

208
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:49,580
not for arguing against her Majesty

209
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:50,980
about using unqualified person.

210
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:52,700
She punished me

211
00:11:52,700 --> 00:11:54,900
for being arrogant,

212
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:58,540
not for being straightforward.

213
00:12:08,420 --> 00:12:09,580
Thank you for your insight.

214
00:12:10,820 --> 00:12:13,980
Even if we can’t meet again in the future,

215
00:12:15,300 --> 00:12:16,700
I shall never forget what you told me today.

216
00:12:37,860 --> 00:12:39,820
Nowadays in the standard of talents selection

217
00:12:39,940 --> 00:12:42,180
words and expressions accounts for too much,

218
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:44,020
political analysis and suggestions too little.

219
00:12:46,260 --> 00:12:48,700
That is to put the cart before the horse

220
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:49,980
in terms of selecting talents.

221
00:12:50,300 --> 00:12:52,500
But changing the standard of talents selection

222
00:12:52,540 --> 00:12:53,780
involves too much,

223
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:55,620
it is not available at this moment.

224
00:12:56,500 --> 00:12:58,500
I am willing to give a try.

225
00:12:58,500 --> 00:13:00,220
That is how the academy

226
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:03,300
should train students.

227
00:13:04,700 --> 00:13:06,700
= Keep learning in your heart =
One thing Fan Zhongyan said impressed me most.

228
00:13:07,220 --> 00:13:08,020
He said

229
00:13:08,540 --> 00:13:10,220
the worries intellectuals have about the country

230
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:11,420
is more important than words and expressions.

231
00:13:11,740 --> 00:13:13,020
But now many students

232
00:13:13,020 --> 00:13:15,780
are proud of quoting words from classics

233
00:13:15,780 --> 00:13:16,860
and feel superior.

234
00:13:17,180 --> 00:13:18,340
How can such students

235
00:13:18,340 --> 00:13:19,740
understand the life of common people

236
00:13:19,980 --> 00:13:21,860
and sympathize with those who suffered from difficulties

237
00:13:21,940 --> 00:13:24,740
once they take the office?

238
00:13:34,180 --> 00:13:36,020
Fan Zhongyan has both talent and good virtue,

239
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:38,740
why should he settle down under the director

240
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:40,660
of Nanjing Academy who thinks nothing but utility?

241
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:42,660
If he can be in charge of the academy,

242
00:13:42,980 --> 00:13:45,020
he can change the common practice of the academy,

243
00:13:45,380 --> 00:13:46,820
and correct scholars’ spirit of that place.

244
00:13:47,380 --> 00:13:48,540
Why don’t you reform

245
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:50,060
the Nanjing Academy

246
00:13:50,260 --> 00:13:51,660
as the Magistrate of the Academy

247
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:54,620
and change the director of the Academy?

248
00:13:56,220 --> 00:14:00,980
= Nanjing Academy =

249
00:14:09,580 --> 00:14:10,180
Sir,

250
00:14:10,940 --> 00:14:12,220
you can’t park your carriage here.

251
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:14,340
Do you know where it is?

252
00:14:14,940 --> 00:14:15,820
It’s the academy.

253
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:17,300
Normal people like you

254
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:18,220
can’t go inside.

255
00:14:18,980 --> 00:14:20,180
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
Come on, come on.

256
00:14:20,180 --> 00:14:21,340
Go away.

257
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:24,860
Stop looking at it.

258
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:26,060
The proctor will be here soon.

259
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:26,900
Go away!

260
00:14:30,620 --> 00:14:31,340
Hurry,

261
00:14:31,980 --> 00:14:33,500
go away with your carriage.

262
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:35,100
Come on, give it to me.

263
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:46,500
Sir.

264
00:14:48,780 --> 00:14:49,420
Hurry.

265
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:50,820
Take your carriage away.

266
00:14:51,260 --> 00:14:52,540
Don’t disturb the students.

267
00:14:53,940 --> 00:14:56,380
All I have in my carriage are the necessities for

268
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:57,220
food, travelling and accommodation.

269
00:14:57,220 --> 00:14:58,260
How can I disturb

270
00:14:58,260 --> 00:14:59,540
the students?

271
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:02,220
They are learning virtues and philosophies of sages.

272
00:15:04,740 --> 00:15:07,700
I, entrusted by Magistrate Yan,

273
00:15:07,900 --> 00:15:10,180
am hired to teach in the academy.

274
